# **Users Components**
1. Farmer
- Registers/Logs in  chooses role: Farmer.
- Uploads produce info  quantity of plantain harvested, location, expected delivery date.
- Gets listed on Marketplace  processors can see available raw plantain.
- Smart contract agreement  farmer & processor agree on price & supply terms.
- Delivery confirmation  once delivery is made, blockchain records it.
- Payment release  Paystack/crypto wallet auto-releases funds when terms are met.

2. Processor
- Registers/Logs in  chooses role: Processor.
- Browses Marketplace  views farmers plantain offers.
- Initiates smart contract  selects farmer, agrees on supply terms.
- Processes raw plantain  converts to flour, based on quality grade
- Updates product info  batch number, quality, storage, blockchain ID.
- Lists finished goods  products go to E-commerce Shop for distributors/consumers.

3. Distributor
- Registers/Logs in  chooses role: Distributor.
- Views available processed goods  flour packs.
- Places bulk orders  via shop (checkout with Paystack/HBAR).
- Delivery scheduling  logistics tracked via dashboard.
- Blockchain traceability  ensures products came from trusted processors.
- Manages inventory  updates sales & distribution channels.

 4. Consumer
- Browses Shop  sees finished goods (plantain flour).
- Checks traceability  clicks Blockchain ID to verify origin & supply chain.
- Adds to cart & pays  Paystack (Naira) or wallet (HBAR).
- Receives order  delivery updates visible on dashboard.
- Leaves review/feedback  boosts trust for future buyers.

5. Admin / Platform Owner
- Onboards new users  verifies farmers, processors, distributors.
- Monitors contracts & orders  ensures supply chain is fair and transparent.
- Runs analytics  identifies demand-supply gaps, trends.
- Supports users  via chat/FAQ/helpdesk.
